Method

Fix the best data scale from EXP1 (or num_classes=16, instances=80, steps=1500 if EXP1 not yet run).
Sweep, per loss:

Fréchet: lambda_frechet ∈ {0.1, 0.3, 1.0}
Triangle: lambda_triangle ∈ {0.1, 0.3, 1.0}
vMF: lambda_vmf ∈ {0.002, 0.01, 0.05}

Include the λ=0 baseline point once (that is just notebook 00).
Seeds {0, 1} to keep the count at 3 losses × 3 λ × 2 seeds = 18 runs.
Plot R@1-instance vs λ per loss, with the baseline as a horizontal band (mean ± std). A loss “wins” only if its best λ clears the baseline band.
